@startuml
title 嵌入式 Linux 套框分层架构图

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #4D4D4D
  FontColor #1F1F1F
}

rectangle "应用与业务域\nApplication Domain" #E8F4FF {
  rectangle "业务进程层\n- tcu_logic\n- tcu_pile_controller\n- tcu_meter\n- tcu_comm\n- logger/daemon" #D9ECFF {
    rectangle "中间件与运行时\n- MQTT Broker/Client\n- cJSON\n- IPC/libv2gshm\n- 配置与日志组件" #ECF7FF {
      rectangle "Linux 用户空间\n- init/systemd\n- 网络与运维工具\n- 标准C/C++运行库" #F3FBFF {
        rectangle "Linux 内核空间\n- 调度/内存/VFS/网络/IPC" #FFF6E8 {
          rectangle "设备驱动层\n- CAN/UART/RS485/Ethernet/GPIO/Watchdog/Storage" #FFF1DC {
            rectangle "BSP 与启动链路\n- DTS/Board Config\n- U-Boot/Kernel/RootFS" #F7F7F7 {
              rectangle "硬件平台\n- ARM SoC\n- CAN/485收发器\n- eMMC/Flash\n- 网口/4G模块" #EFEFEF
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

note right
分层原则：
1) 上层仅依赖下层提供的稳定接口
2) 协议适配与业务逻辑解耦
3) 故障优先局部隔离，避免全局影响
end note

@enduml

